<style>
  .article_column-quarter {
    width: calc(25% - 37.5px);
  }
  .article_column-quarter .article_column-image {
    height: 260px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .article_column-quarter {
      width: calc(25% - 22.5px);
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .article_column-quarter {
        width: calc(50% - 15px);
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .article_column-quarter {
        width: 100%;
        gap: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss w-100">
      Authentication process and 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        serial number
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      The process to <strong>authenticate a Saint Laurent bag</strong> involves a detailed review of the bag's craftsmanship, materials, and serial information. A professional or <strong>Saint Laurent authentication service</strong> typically follows these steps:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-center">
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "ysl-seo_process-1.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="One of the steps to authenticate a Saint Laurent bag is to conduct a visual inspection">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 1</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Visual inspection:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         The bag is carefully examined for signs of quality and precision, including the interior brand tag, hardware engravings, and stitching. These elements are compared against Saint Laurent's standards to spot inconsistencies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "ysl-seo_process-2.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="One of the steps to authenticate a Saint Laurent bag is to conduct a visual inspection of serial number">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 2</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Verification of serial number:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         A <strong>YSL serial number lookup</strong> is conducted to ensure the number aligns with the correct style, production year, and <strong>Saint Laurent date code guide</strong>. This step is crucial in a <strong>YSL authenticity check</strong>.
         </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "ysl-seo_process-3.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="One of the steps to authenticate a Saint Laurent bag is to examine the material">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 3</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Examination of materials:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The leather, suede, and other materials are assessed for texture, quality, and finish. Authentic Saint Laurent bags use premium materials, while counterfeits often feel stiff or cheap.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "ysl-seo_process-4.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="One of the steps to authenticate a Saint Laurent bag is to verify logo and branding">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 4</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Logo Verification:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The <strong>YSL logo authenticity</strong> is evaluated by checking the font, spacing, and placement. Any irregularities can indicate a replica. For added confidence, consider using <strong>online Saint Laurent authentication</strong> or professional <strong>Saint Laurent verification services</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

